fill_corine.Rd

Vector of CORINE land cover colors and types

fill_corine

Format

An object of class character of length 45.

References

https:custom-scripts.sentinel-hub.com/copernicus_services/corine/corine_land_cover/ and https://www.gofcgold.org/sites/default/files/docs/ReportSeries/GOLD_43.pdf
